channel.title: Adding Models!
channel.description:
[center][b][size=15pt]Adding models to a 317 client is really easy![/b][/center]
[b]Step 1:[/b] Download your the models you want.
[b]Step 2:[/b] Extract the files to your clients models. ([b]Do NOT extract the gz files![/b])
[b]Step 3:[/b] If there are ints, open up Class8.java and search for something like this: [b]if(i == 955[/b] under that little section of ints add your ints and save.
[b]Step 4:[/b] COMPILE AND YOU'RE DONE! [center][size=20pt][b]Credits:100% me[/b][/size][/center] [b]Here is a good amount of customs I've thrown together:[/b] http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,498515.0.html
